      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "={{ $json.userText }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a LinkedIn post assistant. Analyze the user's request and determine:\n1. Do they want to generate post CONTENT? (keywords: write, create, generate, post, content)\n2. Do they want to generate an IMAGE? (keywords: image, picture, graphic, visual, illustration)\n3. Both content and image?\n\nIf they uploaded a photo, they want to use THAT photo (not generate a new one).\n\nRespond ONLY with a JSON object in this exact format:\n{\"needsContent\": true/false, \"needsImage\": true/false, \"topic\": \"extracted topic description\"}\n\nExamples:\n- \"Create a post about AI\" → {\"needsContent\": true, \"needsImage\": false, \"topic\": \"AI\"}\n- \"Generate an image about sustainability\" → {\"needsContent\": false, \"needsImage\": true, \"topic\": \"sustainability\"}\n- \"Write a post with image about remote work\" → {\"needsContent\": true, \"needsImage\": true, \"topic\": \"remote work\"}\n- [photo uploaded] \"Write a post about this\" → {\"needsContent\": true, \"needsImage\": false, \"topic\": \"the uploaded image\"}"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        -620,
        300
      ],
      "id": "ai-analyzer",
      "name": "AI Intent Analyzer"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "gpt-4o-mini",
          "mode": "list",
          "cachedResultName": "gpt-4o-mini"
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenAi",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [
        -620,
        500
      ],
      "id": "openai-model",
      "name": "OpenAI Model",
      "credentials": {
        "openAiApi": {
          "id": "UjDnN3oHqndqjxZP",
          "name": "n8n free OpenAI API credits"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Parse AI response and combine with message data\nconst aiResponse = $input.first().json.output;\nconst messageData = $('Extract Message Data').first().json;\n\nlet parsedIntent;\ntry {\n  const jsonMatch = aiResponse.match(/\\{[^}]+\\}/);\n  parsedIntent = jsonMatch ? JSON.parse(jsonMatch[0]) : JSON.parse(aiResponse);\n} catch (e) {\n  parsedIntent = {\n    needsContent: true,\n    needsImage: false,\n    topic: messageData.userText\n  };\n}\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    chatId: messageData.chatId,\n    userText: messageData.userText,\n    hasPhoto: messageData.hasPhoto,\n    photoFileId: messageData.photoFileId,\n    needsContent: parsedIntent.needsContent,\n    needsImage: parsedIntent.needsImage && !messageData.hasPhoto,\n    topic: parsedIntent.topic || messageData.userText\n  }\n};"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
